# Hibiscus (Zobo) ðŸŒº

## Scientific Name
Hibiscus sabdariffa

## Health Benefits
- Supports blood pressure regulation
- Heart health
- Antioxidant-rich
- Improves circulation

## Preparation
Boil dried zobo petals for 10 minutes. Drink warm or cold.

## Dosage
1 cup once daily

## Safety
Avoid excessive use if blood pressure is already low.
